---
title: Mediterranean Chicken Salad with Green Beans and Black Olive-Sherry Vinaigrette
description: Aged sherry vinegar is full of nutty, complex intensity. Whisked into a garlicky black olive vinaigrette, it gives this salad both elegance and depth. Little nuggets of beans contrast crisp green beans for textural intrigue, while bright parsley and briny olives add pops of flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mediterranean-chicken-salad-3ef88e9b.jpg
